body_html:
Same issue running TensorFlow Lite iOS Demo App. Followed all directions on https://www.tensorflow.org/mobile/tflite/demo_ios, build succeeds on my iPhone but error at runtime as shown below. iPhone screen remains black, or with camera (no classifications) and unresponsive 'Freeze Frame' below camera.

  • Xcode 9.3
  • MacOS High Sierra 10.13.4
  • iPhone 6s with iOS 11.3
